Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'MRI pelvic floor' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
Then I go to Page 03 and select 'Yes' in Contrast enhanced
Then I go to Page 08 of Pelvic MRI
And I click on 'Finding' radio button
And dropdown below 'Finding' is enabled

When I select 'Sigmoid diverticular disease' from the dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization I' tab is preselected

And 'Sigmoid diverticulosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Diverticulitis' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Sigmoid diverticulosis' radio button
Then 'Multiple' radio button is enabled
And 'Single' radio button is enabled

And 'Upper third' checkbox is enabled
And 'Middle third' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lower third' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Diverticulitis' radio button
Then 'Intestinal wall thickening' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mesenteric fat obliteration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Increased contrast enhancement of intestinal wall' checkbox is enabled
And 'Covered perforation' radio button is enabled
And 'Free perforation' radio button is enabled

And 'Abscess' checkbox is enabled
And 'Free fluid' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fistula' checkbox is enabled
And 'Phlegmons' checkbox is enabled
And 'Stenosis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Peritonitis' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Free perforation' radio button
Then 'Diameter' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field 'Diameter'
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field 'Diameter'
Then the number is accepted

When I select 'Intestinal wall thickening' checkbox
Then 'Focal' radio button is enabled
And 'Ubiquitous' radio button is enabled
And 'Maximum wall thickness' input field is enabled
And 'Mesenteric fat obliteration' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field 'Maximum wall thickness'
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field 'Maximum wall thickness'
Then the number is accepted

When I enter '1' in the input field 'Mesenteric fat obliteration'
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field 'Mesenteric fat obliteration'
Then the number is accepted

When I select 'Free perforation' radio button
Then 'Free air' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Abscess' checkbox
Then 'Maximum diameter' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field 'Maximum diameter'
Then 'Micro abscess (≤ 10 mm)' auto-checked radio button is selected
When I enter '10' in the input field 'Maximum diameter'
Then 'Micro abscess (≤ 10 mm)' auto-checked radio button is selected


When I enter '11' in the input field 'Maximum diameter'
Then 'Macro abscess (> 10 mm)' auto-checked radio button is selected
And 'Possible CT-guided drainage' checkbox is selected

When I select 'Fistula' checkbox
Then 'Urinary bladder' radio button is enabled
And 'Intestine' radio button is enabled
And 'Uterus' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Stenosis' checkbox
Then 'Ileus' checkbox is enabled

